Hi CD,

Over the last months I have upgraded the SDS mk4 swerve module into 3 motors module with easy and less maintenance.

We had 2 iterations/versions:

V1 - adding a motor.

V2 - making a larger wheelbase with easy maintenance.

Highlights of the 3 motors module include:

  • double mechanical power
  • better pressure distribution
  • larger wheelbase
  • taking out motors spacers without cutting any shaft
  • less maintenance
  • easy maintenance

V1 -

WhatsApp Image 2023-07-22 at 20.44.071536×2048 401 KB

WhatsApp Image 2023-07-22 at 20.44.051536×2048 357 KB

V2 -

swerve (V2)1575×2048 414 KB

swerve (2)860×584 91.5 KB

swerve (1)877×573 117 KB

These days were working on fully aluminum modules (yeah the parts in the photos are printed ) - We will update you!
So stay updated

Available and happy to answer your questions
